IndexDen,is,a,hosted,full,text,search,database,Developers,can,offload,to,IndexDen,s,search,as,a,service,for,real,time,searches,The,service,is,IndexTank,compatible,and,is,tuned,for,full,text,searches,Developers,can,provide,advanced,searching,such,as,scoring,functions,snippet,highlighting,fuzzy,and,faceted,search,In,addition,to,performing,searches,the,API,can,also,be,used,to,add,documents,to,the,index,tune,scoring,functions,and,implement,category,search,such,as,item,type,The,API,returns,serialized,JSON,and,has,client,libraries,for,Python,PHP,Ruby,and,Java